---
/*
  Pricing block: three cards with a featured center card.
  Uses Tailwind utilities to match spacing/typography of the demo.
*/
---
<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-12">
    <h2 id="pricing" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Pricing & Services</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Choose the plan that fits your business. Usage costs (API, compute, integrations) are billed separately.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 (starter) -->
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white border-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 
         hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] hover:border-purple-700">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Marketing</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold">7% <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500">ROAS</span> + $1750 <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500"> / mo</span></div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Best Value</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Pay Return on Ad-Spend + Retainer</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Marketing Automations (Email + CRM) Included</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Ad Management & Content Creation Included</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Google Ads, Facebook Ads, Youtube Ads</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> SEO Expertise for Consistent Clients</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200" href="#signup">Register now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured Card -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white pricing-featured border-2 border-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 
         hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] hover:border-purple-500">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Data Analysis</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">$1800-3500<span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500">/ month</span></div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Best Value</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> 3-8 Analytics Dashboards with Secured Access</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Up to 7 Data Integrations including APIs and Files</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Advanced AI Analytics with Mathematical Rigor</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Monthly Insight Reports in PPTX format</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Priority Support with 72 hour SLA</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-md bg-brand hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold" href="#signup">Register now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 (enterprise) -->
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white border-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 
         hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] hover:border-purple-700">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Automations</div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold">$1250 <span class="text-base font-medium text-slate-500"> / automation / mo</span></div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Best Value</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Unlimited Possibilities; Automate Anything</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> MCP Server Setup with Agentic Task Execution</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Integrate with APIs, Tabular Data, and More</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Enhaced Security & Compliance</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Save Time, Resources, and Workload</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200" href="#signup">Register now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
